lead_paragraph: Jordan Morris, a member of the U.S. national team, is skipping his senior season at Stanford and will train with Werder Bremen starting Sunday at the German team's camp in Belek, Turkey.

headline.main: Jordan Morris to Skip Senior Season at Stanford
